{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/extras/SlimeBrew_img_brew_beer.gif?t=1737095599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bounce, Merge, and Evolve Slimes to Brew the Ultimate Beer!</strong> \ud83c\udf7a</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal? Create delicious beer from bouncing slimes! Brew, brew, brew, and drink, drink, drink to your heart's content! \ud83c\udf7a\ud83c\udf7a\ud83c\udf7a</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/extras/SlimeBrew_img_control.gif?t=1737095599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Simple Controls!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move the crane to drop slimes\u2014it's that easy! When slimes of the same color touch, they merge and evolve. Watch them wobble and bounce as they transform!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/extras/SlimeBrew_img_gameover.gif?t=1737095599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>But Be Careful!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stack too many slimes, and they might overflow! If they spill over... \ud83d\udca5GAME OVER!\ud83d\udca5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/extras/SlimeBrew_img_drink_beer.gif?t=1737095599\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drink and Earn!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each time you drink a beer, you earn coins.\ud83d\udcb0 The more you drink, the more coins you collect, allowing you to become rich! Coins can be used to customize your name tag displayed on the leaderboard and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Variety of Online Leaderboards</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete against other players in a variety of rankings:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>All-Time Score Ranking</strong> \ud83d\udc51</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Daily Score Ranking</strong> \ud83c\udf89(Earn coin rewards after rankings are finalized.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Monthly Score Ranking</strong> \ud83c\udf8a(Earn coin rewards after rankings are finalized.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Richest Player Ranking</strong> \ud83d\udcb0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>First Drink RTA Rankings</strong> (Race to drink your first beer as fast as possible.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ready to craft beer and climb the leaderboard? Cheers! \ud83c\udf7b<br><br><br>[<strong>Video Streaming Guidelines</strong>]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gameplay videos of this game can be streamed or shared by individuals or organizations alike. Monetization is also permitted. However, please refrain from any use that may cause viewers to mistake your content for official material or that could harm the game's image.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Please note that these guidelines are subject to change or updates without prior notice.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737095599","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737095599","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/acf343c76f2117c37cebd6ffa871f089334928c3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737095599","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370930/acf343c76f2117c37cebd6ffa871f089334928c3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737095599","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description"